ly the resolved janino artifact and its transitive commons-compiler dependency; no extra dependency, Docker image, environment variable, or system property is needed for meaningful coverage.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"The existing compile failure is from a stale test importing org.codehaus.janino.util.iterator.Iterables, which is no longer present in janino 3.1.0. Prefer public Janino APIs such as ExpressionEvaluator, ScriptEvaluator, ClassBodyEvaluator, SimpleCompiler, and Compiler. If testing iterator utilities is still desired, they moved under the transitive commons-compiler package org.codehaus.commons.compiler.util.iterator, but coverage should primarily exercise Janino behavior.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"AntCompilerAdapter usage would require optional/provided Ant dependencies, but Ant integration is not necessary for meaningful Janino coverage.\",\n    \"Tests that execute generated classes may hit native-image dynamic class loading limitations; existing tests already account for this as runtime behavior, not pre-generation setup.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0e54ccdaf589ebe5016a429b45efe881968aaf5f69cebac78b\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1003, "output": 478, "cacheRead": 18944, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 20425, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782750014716, "responseId": "resp_0e54ccdaf589ebe5016a429b3f21a88196b9f79841c94f748f"}}
